       B(mumax(5))     = 0. , 0.
       C(mumax(5))     = 0. , 0.

       * parameter Exponent:
       Exponent     = 1.0 , 1.0
       Xmax(0) = 0., 0.
       Xmax(1)        = 0.1, 0.1     # [1]
       Exponent(1)     = 1.0 , 1.0
       B(Exponent(1))     = 0. , 0.
