DopingDependence:
{   
        formula = 1 ,   1       # [1]   
  * If formula=1, model suggested by Masetti et al. is used:
  * mu_dop = mumin1 exp(-Pc/N) + (mu_const - mumin2)/(1+(N/Cr)^alpha)
  *                             - mu1/(1+(Cs/N)^beta)
  * with mu_const from ConstantMobility

       * parameter mumin1:
        mumin1  = 144.0 ,        46.0    # [cm2/Vs]
        Xmax(0) = 0., 0.
        Xmax(1) = 0.1, 0.1
